# --- Rust ---
target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak

# --- Local RSI fetch cache (used during parser development to inspect
# real RSI HTML/JSON without re-fetching). Contains fully-rendered
# pages from RSI which may include account-private data when fetched
# with a session cookie — must never be committed.
.rsi-fetch/

# --- Design handoff bundles fetched at development time. The Claude
# Design tooling exports a tar.gz of HTML/JSX prototypes; we extract
# locally as a reference but it's large (~1.4 MB) and regenerable on
# demand, so it shouldn't live in the repo.
design/**/_fetched/

