# --- Generated ---
# `packages/api-client-ts/src/generated/schema.ts` is the only file
# under `generated/`. It IS committed — the `openapi-drift` CI job
# regenerates it from the live OpenAPI spec and fails the build if
# the committed copy is out of sync. Web-side typecheck depends on
# the committed copy too. Keep this directory tracked.
